OL,3,CRhun ap Iorwerth set to become Plaid
OL,4,CCymru's first premier of Wales
OL,6,FRhun ap Iorwerth, the leader of Plaid
OL,7,FCymru, looks set to become the next
OL,8,FFirst Minister of Wales after his
OL,9,Fparty won the most seats in a historic
OL,10,FWelsh Parliament election.
OL,12,FWith the vote scheduled to take place
OL,13,Fon Tuesday, Mr ap Iorwerth is expected
OL,14,Fto have the most support behind him to
OL,15,Fbecome the next leader of the country.
OL,17,FHis party won the largest bloc in the
OL,18,FWelsh Parliament in the election, but
OL,19,Ffell short of a majority with 43
OL,20,FMembers of the Senedd (MSs).
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
