OL,3,CRhun ap Iorwerth set to become Plaid
OL,4,CCymru's first premier of Wales
OL,6,FMr ap Iorwerth, who said he will seek
OL,7,Fto form a minority government, could
OL,8,Fbecome the first Plaid Cymru MS to
OL,9,Flead Wales.
OL,11,FBorn in South Wales, the 53-year-old
OL,12,Fgrew up on Anglesey and was educated
OL,13,Fat Ysgol David Hughes and later
OL,14,FCardiff University, where he graduated
OL,15,Fin politics and Welsh.
OL,17,FA former BBC journalist and married
OL,18,Ffather-of-three, he made the move into
OL,19,Fpolitics and became a Member of the
OL,20,FSenedd in 2013 after winning a by-
OL,21,Felection in Ynys Mon.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
