PN,30403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1778551406
OL,3,CRhun ap Iorwerth set to become Plaid
OL,4,CCymru's first premier of Wales
OL,6,FHe took over leadership of his party
OL,7,Funopposed in 2023 after a stint as
OL,8,Fdeputy.
OL,10,FHe stepped into the role during a
OL,11,Ftroubled period for the party after
OL,12,Fhis predecessor, Adam Price, resigned
OL,13,Fin the wake of a report finding there
OL,14,Fwas a culture of sexual harassment,
OL,15,Fbullying and misogyny in Plaid Cymru.
OL,17,FMr ap Iorwerth is in favour of Welsh
OL,18,Findependence and previously said his
OL,19,Fparty would use time in government to
OL,20,Fmake the case for an independent Wales.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
