PN,30404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1778551406
OL,3,CRhun ap Iorwerth set to become Plaid
OL,4,CCymru's first premier of Wales
OL,6,FHowever, he ruled out a referendum in
OL,7,Fthe first term of a Plaid Cymru
OL,8,Fgovernment.
OL,10,FIn the vote on Tuesday, Mr ap Iorwerth
OL,11,Fwill have the support of the Wales
OL,12,FGreen Party's two MSs, Welsh Green
OL,13,Fleader Anthony Slaughter has said, as
OL,14,Fwell as Plaid Cymru's 43 members.
OL,16,FWales has been led by a Labour first
OL,17,Fminister since the Welsh Parliament
OL,18,Fwas established more than two decades
OL,19,Fago.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/5
