OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1778551406
OL,3,CRhun ap Iorwerth set to become Plaid
OL,4,CCymru's first premier of Wales
OL,6,FBaroness Eluned Morgan, the outgoing
OL,7,Ffirst minister, resigned from her role
OL,8,Fas Welsh Labour leader after losing
OL,9,Fher seat in the Senedd election.
OL,11,FKen Skates, who scraped in as the
OL,12,Fsixth and last MS to win a seat in
OL,13,FFflint Wrecsam, will serve as the
OL,14,Fparty's interim leader until a full
OL,15,Fleadership contest takes place.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/5
